</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_210" id="104r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_210_r1l12">Den von Sweinfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_210_r1l13"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>Fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> als Jr </del> Vns 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </del> hat <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der <expan>Bıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> von <expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l14"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / von der fehde vnd <expan>veyntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe . da ſeın <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l15"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ~ der von Bıkembach vnd eẅr / <expan>Deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> brıefs wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l16">ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / Darınn Jr ſeiner <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l17">wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan> / VVolten wır niht <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l18">das ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> tun / Vnd daʒ Jr mit <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l19">ın <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd on fehde ſein vnd <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> möchtet / das ſehen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l20">wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teıls <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd deẅht vns / eẅr vnd des lands nucʒe ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l21">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Lucye </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_210" id="104r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Sweinfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> von der fehde und
                                <expan>veyntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die da sein <expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>, der von Bikembach und ewr,
                                <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> briefs wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, darinn ir seiner
                            <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan>, wolten wir niht
                            <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, wir <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> das zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        tun. Und daz ir mit <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> in
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und on fehde sein und
                                <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan> möchtet, das sehen wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teils <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        und dewht uns ewr und des lands nucze sein. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Lucye.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
